5) 'Photograph of 'Sunday' group, 12" x 10" size No 41444-1. Group of five, Miss Neilson sitting on table with left arm round shoulders of old man at her side, man with beard sitting at her right, another man with beard & a young man sitting behind her'. 4cm x 5cm.

10) 'Photograph of 'Sunday' group, 12" x 10" size No 41444-7, Miss Neilson sitting on garden seat touching Mr Terry on shoulder, he leaning over back of seat watching her'. 4cm x 5cm.

11) 'Photograph of 'Sunday' group, whole plate size No 41444-9, nun sitting at left watching group of Miss Neilson & four men at table. Miss Neilson holding playing card in left hand & resting right hand on back of chair'. 3cm x 3cm.

scopeContent.description:
1) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40524-9. Group of two, Mr Benson standing with both arms raised looking up, a man lying on ground at feet'. 3cm x 3cm.

2) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40524-10. Group of three in 'Julius Caesar'. A man standing profile holding hand of another man in both his this man raising goblet in right hand. A boy standing at right of picture, holding pitcher'. 3cm x 3cm.

3) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40524-11. Group in 'Julius Caesar'. A man seated with right arm pointed back at ghost standing behind him to his right, other men lying asleep on ground'. 3cm x 3cm.

4) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40524-12. Group in 'Julius Caesar'. A man kneeling on left knee with left hand to face & right arm stretched behind him, ghost standing behind him to his right. Men lying asleep on ground'. 3cm x 3cm.

5) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40524-13. Group in 'Julius Caesar'. A man kneeling on ground with sword pointed to chest, right arm stretched behing him. Group of men bearing away the body of a man on their shoulders'. 3cm x 3cm.

6) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40524-14. Group in 'Julius Caesar'. Body of man lying on ground, a man bending over him covering him with cloak. Three other men standing watching him'. 3cm x 3cm.

7) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, cabinet size No 40524-16. Group in 'Julius Caesar'. Man & woman standing together, she with her arms around him, looking up at him'. 3cm x 2cm.

8) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, cabinet size No 40525-19. Group of two in 'A Merchant of Venice'. Woman in light dress, seated on seat, looking down at girl kneeling'. 3cm x 2cm.

9) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40525-10. Group in 'A Merchant of Venice'. A man standing at left of picture, half covering woman beside him with cloak, a man standing in centre pointing with his left arm, two men at right holding casket'. 3cm x 3cm.

10) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40525-11. Group in 'A Merchant of Venice'. Mrs Benson as 'Portia' standing at table with right hand raised looking round at old man 'Shylock'. Two men standing other side of table, one with hands on chest & the other standing behind him with hand on shoulder'. 3cm x 3cm.

11) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40525-12. Group in 'A Merchant of Venice'. Old man 'Shylock' sitting at table looking round at man. Mrs Benson as 'Portia' leaning on table watching him sign paper. Two men standing other side of table clasping hands, other figures all grouped round'. 3cm x 3cm.

12) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40525-13. Group of four in 'A Merchant of Venice'. Mr Benson as 'Shylock' standing at left of picture with arms folded, a man standing in black velvet robes with hands clasped looking at him. Two other men standing'. 3cm x 3cm.

13) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40525-14. Group of five in 'A Merchant of Venice'. Man & woman standing together in centre of picture, she looking round holding the hand of another man at left. Another man & woman standing hand in hand at right of picture'. 3cm x 3cm.

14) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40525-15. Group in 'A Merchant of Venice'. Mr Benson as 'Shylock' at left of picture face turned away, right arm out. Woman in cap & gown sitting full face at table Mrs Benson as 'Portia' standing looking at 'Shylock'. Boy in black velvet suit sitting on ground looking up at man, other figures all grouped round'. 3cm x 3cm.

15) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, whole plate size No 40525-16. Group in 'A Merchant of Venice'. Mrs Benson as 'Portia' standing holding hand of man in both hers, looking up at him man & women standing facing each other in centre, three men at right of picture'. 3cm x 3cm.

16) 'Photograph of Mr F R Benson's Company, cabinet size No 40525-18. Group of two men standing one with hat on holding long staff'. 3cm x 2cm.
